T_ID['insomnia']='<b>insomnia:</b> recurring problems in falling or staying asleep. (p. 103)</p>';
T_ID['instinct']='<b>instinct:</b> a complex behavior that is rigidly patterned throughout a species and is unlearned. (p. 404)</p>';
