T_ID['intelligence']='<b>intelligence:</b> mental quality consisting of the ability to learn from experience, solve problems, and use knowledge to adapt to new situations. (p. 368)</p>';
T_ID['intelligencequotientiq']='<b>intelligence quotient (IQ):</b> defined originally as the ratio of mental age <i>(ma)</i> to chronological age <i>(ca)</i> multiplied by 100 (thus, IQ &#61; <i>ma/ca</i> &#215; 100). On contemporary intelligence tests, the average performance for a given age is assigned a score of 100. (p. 378)</p>';
