T_ID['interneurons']='<b>interneurons:</b> neurons within the brain and spinal cord that communicate internally and intervene between the sensory inputs and motor outputs. (p. 56)</p>';
T_ID['interpretation']='<b>interpretation:</b> in psychoanalysis, the analyst&#8217;s noting supposed dream meanings, resistances, and other significant behaviors and events in order to promote insight. (p. 653)</p>';
