T_ID['kinesthesis']='<b>kinesthesis:</b> [kin-ehs-THEE-sehs] the system for sensing the position and movement of individual body parts. (p. 257)</p>';
T_ID['language']='<b>language:</b> our spoken, written, or signed words and the ways we combine them to communicate meaning. (p. 349)</p>';
