T_ID['lobotomy']='<b>lobotomy:</b> a psychosurgical procedure once used to calm uncontrollably emotional or violent patients. The procedure cut the nerves connecting the frontal lobes to the emotion-controlling centers of the inner brain. (p. 682)</p>';
